 <description>&lt;p&gt;It is a Trans-Siberian right of passage - drinking vodka with Russians on a train in the middle of Siberia.  This video shares a few of the moments I&amp;#39;ll never forget and a few that I can&amp;#39;t really remember.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;object height=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;425&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/emeUXNVwUCM&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;wmode&quot; value=&quot;transparent&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;embed src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/emeUXNVwUCM&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; wmode=&quot;transparent&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;425&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Read the &lt;a href=&quot;/too_much_vodka&quot;&gt;story from this night&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;clear&quot; /&gt;</description>
